caption:
In the season opener of #MoneyTalks, our host Tierra Whack visits Adriana Williams, a designer and seamstress from North Philly who balances a full-time job while building her own lifestyle brand, ADW. The two friends dive into the ways they’ve learned to juggle professional responsibilities, prioritize self-care, and focus on their craft.

Visit venmo.me/moneytalks for resources and more helpful tips.
